  "original_title": "\u0dc4\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0ddc\u0dba\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0d91\u0d9a\u0dca\u0d9a \u0dc0\u0ddb\u0daf\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A doctor was arrested with heroin",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A doctor who ran a private dispensary in Anuradhapura city was arrested with 2260 mg of heroin drugs by the Divisional Crime Investigation Division attached to Anuradhapura Police today (5).",
        "A doctor who runs a private dispensary resident in Pubudupura was arrested in connection with this incident. The police said that he is 67 years old.",
        "According to an information received by an officer of the Anuradhapura headquarters police, a police officer signaled with his hand to stop the van in which the doctor was traveling. The van stopped in front of his house after he was chased after the van did not stop.",
        "The police officers who checked the van found a parcel of heroin and the police said that the person posing as a doctor was a person registered in 2015 and he had previously worked at the Anuradhapura Regional Health Unit.",
        "Along with the arrested person, the van and the heroin parcel have been taken into custody by the police. The suspect was scheduled to be produced before the Anuradhapura Magistrate's Court today.",
        "Chief Inspector W.M.W. According to the direction of Mr. Bandara Weerakoon, Police Sergeant D. GUT Bandara (48317) and D. E. M. N. P. Dissanayake (41406) are conducting investigations."
      ],
